{"type": "article", "id": 25500, "title": "鼻子眼镜架", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-15T07:10:29Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 6, "praise_count": 49, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702144054qhPbuZtILFGUcp04.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这些像鼻子一样的眼镜架让你想在家里也放上一个。它是一个手工瓷器，通过鼻子本身自然的凹凸让眼镜架可以直接架在上面，恰好构成拥有眼睛和鼻子的“面孔”，像是一个小的雕塑。美国的设计团队 OSSO DESIGN 还在上面画出了不同的样式，比如煎鸡蛋、红唇、鱼、眼睛，保留了手工涂鸦的感觉，让它变得很酷。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144051o0grdB3PLMhTp4eF.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144052v9jxlDzrB1Mc3ioX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.48796296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144052ZTS4POrRJY7y90iK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.48796296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144053xg8RWE9ZYGDNdqX1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.48796296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702144053dm20wYDvVKZjkBAI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070214405435orpt9IfXaYbieV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}